2.content:
We may collect the following categories of data:
- first name and last name;
- contact phone number;
- email address;
- travel information: route, date, time, number of passengers;
- messages sent via website forms.

3.content:
Personal data is used for:
- processing enquiries and requests;
- organising and providing transport services;
- communicating with the client;
- internal administration.

4.content:
Data processing is carried out on the basis of:
- performance of a contract or preparation for its conclusion;
- the company's legitimate interests: processing requests, managing services.

7.content:
You have the right to:
- access your personal data;
- request correction of your data;
- request deletion of your data;
- restrict processing;
- object to processing.

5.content:
On the first visit to the website, a cookie banner is displayed, allowing the user to:
- accept all cookies;
- reject all optional cookies;
- configure cookie categories.

Cookies other than strictly necessary ones are not set until consent is obtained.

6.content:
The user may at any time:
- change cookie settings via the website interface;
- delete cookies via browser settings;
- block cookies at the browser level.

Disabling cookies may affect website functionality.

8.content:
The retention period depends on the cookie type:
- session cookies are deleted when the browser is closed;
- persistent cookies are stored for a limited period or until deleted by the user.
